  "description": "A mod that adds more mob heads to the game.",
  "body": "<p><img src=\"https://pedroricardo.net/assets/headed/banner.png\" alt=\"The banner of the mod\" width=\"324\" height=\"180\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h2>📃 About</h2><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>Headed</strong> is a mod that adds more mob heads to decorate your buildings!<br /></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Unlike other head mods and data packs, Headed uses models to render its heads, which means they are not 8x8 player heads!<br /><br /><img src=\"https://pedroricardo.net/assets/headed/all_heads.png\" alt=\"All the heads in the mod's Creative item group\" width=\"324\" height=\"360\" /><br /></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">\n  \n<a title=\"Fabric API on Modrinth\" href=\"https://www.modrinth.com/mod/fabric-api\">Fabric API</a>&nbsp;is also required for both versions.</span></h4>\n<h4>&nbsp;</h4>\n<h2>❗ Other Features</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Coloured sheep heads</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">jeb_ and Toast heads</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Glowing enderman, spider, cave spider and phantom eyes</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Mob head sounds on note blocks</span></li>",
